Emanuel takes on African-American concerns

Mayor needs to win back support

     * [127]print

     *
     *

   Rahm Emanuel

   Mayor Rahm Emanuel greets CTA Red Line commuters at the 95th St.
   station to inform and remind commuters of the Red Line south
   reconstruction project. (Antonio Perez, Chicago Tribune / May 17, 2013)
